      <body>
         <div type="bibliography">
            <p/>
         </div>
         <div type="translation" xml:lang="ru">
            <p>Иисус Христос.</p>
         </div>
         <div type="translation" xml:lang="en">
            <p>Jesus Christ.</p>
         </div>
         <div type="commentary" xml:lang="ru">
            <p>Несколько необычна формула надписи — ожидалось бы стандартное «Иисус Христос побеждает» (см. <ref type="introduction">IV.3.C.e</ref>).</p>
         </div>
         <div type="commentary" xml:lang="en">
            <p>The formula is somewhat unusual - one expects a standard "Jesus Christ is victorious" (see Introduction <ref type="introduction">IV.3.C.e</ref>)</p>
         </div>
         <div type="edition" xml:lang="grc" xml:space="preserve">
            <ab>
               <lb n="1"/><persName type="divine" key="iesous"><name nymRef="Ἰησοῦς"><expan><abbr>Ἰ</abbr><ex>ησοῦ</ex><abbr>ς</abbr></expan></name>
               <lb n="2"/><name nymRef="Χριστός"><expan><abbr>Χ</abbr><ex>ριστό</ex><abbr>ς</abbr></expan></name></persName>.
            </ab>
         </div>
